Si '''San Ramón Bong Revilla, Jr.''' (inianak ''San José María Mortel Bautista'' nen [[September 25|Septiyembre 25]], [[1966]]), sakey [[aktor]] diad [[Totoon Pilipino|Filipino]], TV Host, [[politiko]], tan [[senado diad Pilipino|senador]] ed [[Filipinas|Republika na Filipinas]]. Nen [[2009]], to pian ya legaliyo ed palit diad inter to apilyedo nen '''Bong Revilla'''

==Bilay tan edukasion==

He was born '''José María Mortel Bautista''' to [[Ramon Revilla, Sr.|Jose Acuña Bautista]] (also known as Ramon Revilla) and Azucena Mortel.<ref>[http://www.ramonbongrevillajr.com/profile/ Ramon "Bong" Revilla, Jr. Official Website Public Profile]</ref> In 1979, he finished his [[elementary education]] at [[Jesus Good Shepherd School]] in Palico II, Imus, Cavite.

